        "Crash",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为：起点是FinTech_LedgerService，先到Still状态，然后Still可以流转到Moving运行态，也可能直接连到PaymentGateway？另外崩溃后是直接回LedgerService吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Still确实要双向连接PaymentGateway——可以理解为心跳检测或者状态同步。另外Moving和Still之间要能来回切换，表示服务的启停。Crash之后必须回到LedgerService重新初始化，这是故障恢复的关键路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用stateDiagram-v2把主体框架画出来：LedgerService指向Still作为入口，Still分出两条线——一条到PaymentGateway做状态同步，另一条到Moving进入运行态。Moving和Still之间画双向箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Still",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "运行态这里还需要加上异常分支——Moving应该能进入Crash状态，然后从Crash直接回到LedgerService，形成闭环。这样整个故障处理链路就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：Moving指向Crash的转移，以及Crash返回FinTech_LedgerService的恢复路径。现在整个图有六个状态节点和六条转移线，我检查下连接关系——LedgerService→Still→PaymentGateway，Still↔Moving，Moving→Crash→LedgerService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Still",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
