    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Still到PaymentGateway应该是双向的还是单向的？我刚才说的是心跳检测，那应该是双向同步。但看你描述只画了Still指向PaymentGateway。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "您说得对，我理解错了。实际代码里Still到PaymentGateway是单向的——表示LedgerService初始化后进入静止态，同时向PaymentGateway注册或同步状态。如果不需要双向，当前这样是合理的。需要我改成双向吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用改，单向是对的。LedgerService启动后进入Still，同时通知PaymentGateway自己已就绪。PaymentGateway的响应不体现在这个状态图里。当前结构符合需求，可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Still",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认定稿。最终状态图包含：FinTech_LedgerService作为起点，Still作为中心枢纽连接PaymentGateway和Moving，Moving与Still双向可逆，Moving可转入Crash，Crash唯一出口回到LedgerService完成故障恢复循环。",
